             were indicted for <rs id="t18300916-273-off1384" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300916-273-off1384" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-273-off1384" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300916-273-cd1385" type="crimeDate">7th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-273-off1384 t18300916-273-cd1385"></join>, 1 purse, value 3d.; 26 yards of ribbon, value 6s.; 5 handkerchiefs, value 9s.; 3 pairs of gloves, value 2s.; 1 dozen of buttons, value 6d.; 1 purse, value 1s.; 2 sovereigns, 1 crown, 5 half-crowns, 1 shilling, 1 sixpence, and one 10l. Bank note
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18300916-273-victim2255" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Jones
                  <interp inst="t18300916-273-victim2255" type="surname" value="Jones"></interp>
